  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the efficacy of autologous enriched bone marrow cell
      implantation combined with core decompression to single core decompression for the treatment
      of avascular necrosis of femoral head.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
